<html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:x="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><style>.header1 { background-color: #92D050; color: white; font-weight: bold; } .header2 { background-color: #4A90E2; color: white; font-weight: bold; } .data { vertical-align: top; mso-number-format:'\@'; }</style></head><body><table border="1"><tr><td class="header1" colspan="5" style="text-align:center; font-size: 14px;">21_Mar_SMS1</td></tr><tr><th class="header1">Existing_ServiceName</th><th class="header1">Service_ID</th><th class="header1">SMS_CONTENT</th><th class="header1">Length</th><th class="header1">SQL_Command</th></tr><tr><td class="data">Food & Health</td><td class="data">269</td><td class="data">The Power of a 'Daily' Highlight<br><br>Tip: Each morning, choose one 'highlight' or most important task for your day. Make it your priority.<br><br>Benefits: Helps you to focus your energy and ensures that you end the day with a sense of accomplishment.</td><td class="data">242</td><td class="data">UPDATE sms_content SET date=NOW(), content='The Power of a ''Daily'' Highlight

Tip: Each morning, choose one ''highlight'' or most important task for your day. Make it your priority.

Benefits: Helps you to focus your energy and ensures that you end the day with a sense of accomplishment.' WHERE service_id='269';</td></tr><tr><td class="data">Local Breaking News</td><td class="data">260012000006578</td><td class="data">1. BoZ warns businesses not to reject old banknotes before month-end validity. Old coins remain legal tender and will not be withdrawn after March 31.<br><br>2. Zambia coach Lwandamina states Four Nations Tournament selection requires talent, character & discipline. Zambia, Botswana, Malawi & Zimbabwe compete March 23-31 in Botswana.<br><br>3. Zanaco launched a $35.1M credit line under the Zambia Agribusiness Trade Project Phase II to boost financing for farmers, agribusinesses, and traders.</td><td class="data">484</td><td class="data">UPDATE sms_content SET date=NOW(), content='1. BoZ warns businesses not to reject old banknotes before month-end validity. Old coins remain legal tender and will not be withdrawn after March 31.

2. Zambia coach Lwandamina states Four Nations Tournament selection requires talent, character & discipline. Zambia, Botswana, Malawi & Zimbabwe compete March 23-31 in Botswana.

3. Zanaco launched a $35.1M credit line under the Zambia Agribusiness Trade Project Phase II to boost financing for farmers, agribusinesses, and traders.' WHERE service_id='260012000006578';</td></tr><tr><td class="data">International Breaking News</td><td class="data">260012000006580</td><td class="data">1. US-Israeli war with Iran spotlights AI in defense. Exact use, accuracy, and repercussions are emerging, but AI's full extent in the war remains unknown.<br><br>2. Trump considers winding down Iran war as US sends 2,500 Marines & 3 ships to region. Israel continues strikes on Tehran & Beirut in 4th week of war.<br><br>3. US jury finds Elon Musk misled Twitter shareholders during its purchase. He could face billions in damages and plans to appeal the decision.</td><td class="data">453</td><td class="data">UPDATE sms_content SET date=NOW(), content='1. US-Israeli war with Iran spotlights AI in defense. Exact use, accuracy, and repercussions are emerging, but AI''s full extent in the war remains unknown.

2. Trump considers winding down Iran war as US sends 2,500 Marines & 3 ships to region. Israel continues strikes on Tehran & Beirut in 4th week of war.

3. US jury finds Elon Musk misled Twitter shareholders during its purchase. He could face billions in damages and plans to appeal the decision.' WHERE service_id='260012000006580';</td></tr><tr><td class="data">International Sports Updates</td><td class="data">260012000006583</td><td class="data">1. Manchester United drew with Bournemouth despite leading twice. Maguire's red card was key, as Kroupi's penalty secured the draw, stalling United's Champions League pursuit.<br><br>2. Carlos Alcaraz advanced to Miami Open 3rd round, beating Joao Fonseca 6-4, 6-4.<br><br>3. USA's Jordan Anthony wins 60m world gold, overcoming a "soccer ball"-sized blood clot in his arm that appeared after a misplaced injection.</td><td class="data">403</td><td class="data">UPDATE sms_content SET date=NOW(), content='1. Manchester United drew with Bournemouth despite leading twice. Maguire''s red card was key, as Kroupi''s penalty secured the draw, stalling United''s Champions League pursuit.

2. Carlos Alcaraz advanced to Miami Open 3rd round, beating Joao Fonseca 6-4, 6-4.

3. USA''s Jordan Anthony wins 60m world gold, overcoming a "soccer ball"-sized blood clot in his arm that appeared after a misplaced injection.' WHERE service_id='260012000006583';</td></tr><tr><td class="data">Local Sports</td><td class="data">260012000006584</td><td class="data">1. Zambia's Chipolopolo Boys will face World Champions Argentina in a friendly at La Bombonera on March 31. Argentina confirmed the match.<br><br>2. Forest Myooye beat Barotse Crocs 5-0 in the ABSA Cup preliminary round, qualifying for the Round of 16.<br><br>3. Power Dynamos coach Osward Mutapa says his team "didn't come to the party" after a goalless draw with Leopards meant they failed to extend their league lead.</td><td class="data">408</td><td class="data">UPDATE sms_content SET date=NOW(), content='1. Zambia''s Chipolopolo Boys will face World Champions Argentina in a friendly at La Bombonera on March 31. Argentina confirmed the match.

2. Forest Myooye beat Barotse Crocs 5-0 in the ABSA Cup preliminary round, qualifying for the Round of 16.

3. Power Dynamos coach Osward Mutapa says his team "didn''t come to the party" after a goalless draw with Leopards meant they failed to extend their league lead.' WHERE service_id='260012000006584';</td></tr><tr><td colspan="5">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td class="header2" colspan="5" style="text-align:center; font-size: 14px;">21_Mar_SMS2</td></tr><tr><th class="header2">Existing_ServiceName</th><th class="header2">Service_ID</th><th class="header2">SMS_CONTENT</th><th class="header2">Length</th><th class="header2">SQL_Command</th></tr><tr><td class="data">Food & Health</td><td class="data">269</td><td class="data">Benefits of Paprika<br><br>Tip: Sprinkle paprika over roasted potatoes, chicken, or deviled eggs for a mild, smoky flavour and vibrant colour.<br><br>Benefits: Rich in antioxidants, including carotenoids, which can help protect against cellular damage.</td><td class="data">240</td><td class="data">UPDATE sms_content SET date=NOW(), content='Benefits of Paprika

Tip: Sprinkle paprika over roasted potatoes, chicken, or deviled eggs for a mild, smoky flavour and vibrant colour.

Benefits: Rich in antioxidants, including carotenoids, which can help protect against cellular damage.' WHERE service_id='269';</td></tr><tr><td class="data">Local Breaking News</td><td class="data">260012000006578</td><td class="data">1. Brian Mundubile granted K50,000 police bond after being charged with aiding, abetting, and counselling to commit hate speech.<br><br>2. Muchinga chiefs commended President Hichilema for improving Zambian welfare & pledged land for infrastructure projects.<br><br>3. Opposition leader R. Chabinga vows PF won't be on August 13 ballot due to a stalled leadership legal battle.</td><td class="data">365</td><td class="data">UPDATE sms_content SET date=NOW(), content='1. Brian Mundubile granted K50,000 police bond after being charged with aiding, abetting, and counselling to commit hate speech.

2. Muchinga chiefs commended President Hichilema for improving Zambian welfare & pledged land for infrastructure projects.

3. Opposition leader R. Chabinga vows PF won''t be on August 13 ballot due to a stalled leadership legal battle.' WHERE service_id='260012000006578';</td></tr><tr><td class="data">International Breaking News</td><td class="data">260012000006580</td><td class="data">1. Russian spy unit Center 795, linked to assassinations, exposed. An agent's Google Translate use let FBI read their communications.<br><br>2. Iran struck Gulf oil & gas sites, jolting energy markets. South Africa faces steep economic costs as Middle East tensions continue.<br><br>3. US prosecutors are investigating Colombian President Gustavo Petro over suspected ties to drug traffickers, according to a New York Times report.</td><td class="data">419</td><td class="data">UPDATE sms_content SET date=NOW(), content='1. Russian spy unit Center 795, linked to assassinations, exposed. An agent''s Google Translate use let FBI read their communications.

2. Iran struck Gulf oil & gas sites, jolting energy markets. South Africa faces steep economic costs as Middle East tensions continue.

3. US prosecutors are investigating Colombian President Gustavo Petro over suspected ties to drug traffickers, according to a New York Times report.' WHERE service_id='260012000006580';</td></tr><tr><td class="data">International Sports Updates</td><td class="data">260012000006583</td><td class="data">1. England manager Thomas Tuchel named two expanded squads (35 players) to assess fringe players for World Cup places, citing it as the "least messy" solution before the finals.<br><br>2. Coroner: Ex-boxing champ Ricky Hatton died by hanging, but intention to take his own life cannot be satisfied, inquest concludes.<br><br>3. Jack Draper was beaten by US star Reilly Opelka in straight sets at the Miami Open. Opelka fired down 25 aces in the match.</td><td class="data">439</td><td class="data">UPDATE sms_content SET date=NOW(), content='1. England manager Thomas Tuchel named two expanded squads (35 players) to assess fringe players for World Cup places, citing it as the "least messy" solution before the finals.

2. Coroner: Ex-boxing champ Ricky Hatton died by hanging, but intention to take his own life cannot be satisfied, inquest concludes.

3. Jack Draper was beaten by US star Reilly Opelka in straight sets at the Miami Open. Opelka fired down 25 aces in the match.' WHERE service_id='260012000006583';</td></tr><tr><td class="data">Local Sports</td><td class="data">260012000006584</td><td class="data">1. Zesco United ended their 5-match winless run, beating Nchanga Rangers 1-0 in Week 28 MTN Super League. Abraham Siankombo scored. Leopards held Power Dynamos.<br><br>2. Rory McIlroy will serve elk at the Masters champions dinner, crediting it for fueling his past win.<br><br>3. Judge rebukes legal teams over slow progress in rugby brain injury lawsuits, ongoing for 5 years. They must choose 28 lead claimants by October.</td><td class="data">413</td><td class="data">UPDATE sms_content SET date=NOW(), content='1. Zesco United ended their 5-match winless run, beating Nchanga Rangers 1-0 in Week 28 MTN Super League. Abraham Siankombo scored. Leopards held Power Dynamos.

2. Rory McIlroy will serve elk at the Masters champions dinner, crediting it for fueling his past win.

3. Judge rebukes legal teams over slow progress in rugby brain injury lawsuits, ongoing for 5 years. They must choose 28 lead claimants by October.' WHERE service_id='260012000006584';</td></tr></table></body></html>